Class SimulatedOracle

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.jclal.activelearning.oracle.AbstractOracle

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, IOracle, JCLAL

    public class SimulatedOracle
extends AbstractOracle
    Class that representes an oracle in simulated manner. The class of the selected instances are known previously to the AL process, ie. the class of the unlabeled instances are hidden.
